<br>
I use mana burn when I can, just because it's easier to &quot;Fire and Forget&quot; Qralt.  Then concentrate on Laderial for healing.  <br>
<br>
Anyways, playing with Magelo and AA points, I was a little disappointed in the net effect of raising my Int cap on my mana pool.<br>
<br>
